-----------------Spring Boot--------------
1. If a microservice A is serving two other microservices B nd C then declaring dependencies
in A would automatically add dependencies in B and C.
-----------------Spring Security--------------
1. By default spring security 6 enables form based and HTTP based authentication.

*****For spring security authentication :
---> for loading a user object from the database and providing it to spring security for preforming authentication we
implement spring security provided UserDetailsService Interface.

----> from spring 5.2 onwards spring security will automatically provide the userDetailsService and passwordEncoder
to Authentication Manager.

---> JWT ---> https://www.tutorialspoint.com/spring_security/spring_security_with_jwt.htm
